Beginnings of a NES demake of Zachtronics Industries' design puzzle game "SpaceChem".

The real game's web site is http://www.spacechemthegame.com/

This project is currently experimenting with rendering the editor interface.

Written using Dave Huesby's Linux port (https://bitbucket.org/wookie/neshla) of Brian Provinciano's NESHLA high level assembler (http://neshla.sourceforge.net/).
